# NextJs Page Rules

This rule applies when creating *any new additional* NextJs Pages in /app directory

* ALWAYS use or `@app/layout.tsx` to contain ANY new pages.
* use `@app/page/`  This is so we have the sidebar and header at all times throughout the app.
